caption:
|| Concept ! Mayumi Yong 

okay so I finally did a character sheet I like and it’s because I finally am doing a character ( besides ) Kaida. This is Mayumi, a girl born of the sinner and sinless, damned from fate from the very beginning, she turns into a human eating monster classed only as WENDIGOS but even outside that form, she’s a force to be reckoned with, as her magic is so volatile that it even causes backlash to herself.
